  48:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****       Normal transfers mode is initialized via the standard module and linked-list mode is configur
  49:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****       module.
  50:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c **** 
  51:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****     [..]
  52:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****       Additionally to linked-list capability, all advanced DMA features are managed and configured 
  53:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****       module as extensions to normal mode.
  54:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****       Advanced features are :
  55:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****           (+) Repeated block feature.
