 167:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****     =========================================
 168:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****     [..]
 169:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****           (+) Use HAL_DMA_ConfigChannelAttributes() function to configure DMA channel security and 
 170:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****               (++) Security  : at channel level, at source level and at destination level.
 171:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****               (++) Privilege : at channel level.
 172:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****           (+) Use HAL_DMA_GetConfigChannelAttributes() function to get the DMA channel attributes.
 173:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****           (+) Use HAL_DMA_LockChannelAttributes() function to lock the DMA channel security and pri
 174:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****               configuration. This API can be called once after each system boot.
 175:../Drivers/STM32N6xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32n6xx_hal_dma.c ****               If called again, HAL_DMA_ConfigChannelAttributes() API has no effect.
